Title: Unruhe
Plot: Several kidnappings of young women linked by distorted photographs lead Mulder and Scully to a man who can imprint his darkest fantasies onto undeveloped film and is trying to save the women from the "Howlers".
GuestStars: Pruitt Taylor Vince, William MacDonald, Walter Marsh, Sharon Alexander, Ron Chartier, Michael Cram, Christopher Royal, Michele Melland, Scott Heindl, Angela Donahue
